WEBVTT

00:00.062 --> 00:03.040
My esteemed partner,
Mr Joseph Merceron.

00:03.042 --> 00:05.266
Soon to be your esteemed partner,
gentleman.

00:05.268 --> 00:07.853
He was falsely accused by Hanson
himself because he tried

00:07.855 --> 00:10.238
to stamp out such greed and
brutality!

00:10.240 --> 00:13.158
My reputation within the House has
been utterly ruined.

00:13.160 --> 00:14.718
What exactly would you seek?

00:14.720 --> 00:15.758
Revenge.

00:15.760 --> 00:17.278
Forgery is a hanging offence.

00:17.280 --> 00:19.038
I'll be forced to name these
persons.

00:19.040 --> 00:22.118
I've considered our situation
and believe there's now

00:22.120 --> 00:23.358
only one solution.

00:23.360 --> 00:26.078
Ned was set up and will take down
all who stand by him.

00:26.080 --> 00:29.078
-I will stand by him.
-Stay where you are!
-I warned you what would happen

00:29.080 --> 00:31.038
if you failed to keep him out of
trouble.

00:31.040 --> 00:33.760
Now, if he falls, he takes you with
him.

